data.description: Welcome home to this inviting and spacious two-bedroom, two-bathroom residence. The unit boasts an open floor plan with an abundance of storage and natural light throughout. The primary bedroom includes a large walk-in closet, an ensuite bathroom with double sinks, a separate shower stall, and a soaking bathtub. The gourmet kitchen is perfect for culinary enthusiasts, featuring ample counter space and storage, granite countertops, a separate dining area, and a cozy breakfast nook for leisurely mornings. The family room serves as the heart of the unit, with its large sliding glass door opening to a private ground floor balcony, ideal for outdoor relaxation and offering a beautiful view of the woods. The community offers a wide range of amenities, including an outdoor pool, a clubhouse, secure entrances, and an elevator. This property enjoys a fantastic location with close proximity to shopping, restaurants, trails, Old Town Manassas, Signal Hill Park, as well as easy access to Route 28, Route 66, and the VRE Train Station, making commuting to Northern Virginia and Washington, D.C., a breeze.
